# --- outputs/：忽略全部数据文件；仅跟踪 README.md 与各目录 .gitkeep（保留 q1–q4 结构）---
outputs/*
!outputs/README.md
!outputs/.gitkeep
!outputs/q1/
!outputs/q2/
!outputs/q3/
!outputs/q4/
outputs/q1/*
outputs/q2/*
outputs/q3/*
outputs/q4/*
!outputs/q1/.gitkeep
!outputs/q2/.gitkeep
!outputs/q3/.gitkeep
!outputs/q4/.gitkeep

# --- visualization/：忽略所有图片产物；源码 .py 与导出 .html 保留（含 figures_* 与各 q*）---
visualization/**/*.png
visualization/**/*.jpg
visualization/**/*.jpeg
visualization/**/*.webp
visualization/**/*.gif
visualization/**/*.bmp
visualization/**/*.tif
visualization/**/*.tiff
visualization/**/*.svg
